column2: "Howdareyou howdareyou howdareyou howdareyou howdareyou! Me! Me! You outwitted me, huh?!"
"My omniscience... my Xion... from my hand, it slipped from my hand... ooh, oooh..!"
"...I can't forgive, I can't forgive this. I can't I can't I can't I can't! You bastard, just youuu!!"
"A reaction in the Mothership...?! It's huge... it's not just some Darker! <%me>!"
"...<%me>! You bastard! Just you, I'll! with these hands I'll!"
"Fuha, fuhahahahafuha! Die die die die kill kill I'll kill yooooou!"
"Ha, ha... haa! I finally... caught up...!"
"...Whoa, what the heck is he? I said I'd go ahead, but I didn't hear anything about this!"
"You, you, you bastard! Me! To defy me! This vanquished one! This Luther! This Loser!"
"That solution is unnecessary! The answer is what I desire! Those that won't follow me, DIE!"
